Proposed Changess
Project Setup
Install dependencies: redux-toolkit, react-redux
State Management (Redux)
[NEW] 

store.ts
Configure Redux store.
[NEW] 

cartSlice.ts
State: items, totalAmount, loading, error.
Thunks:
fetchCart: GET /cart/:cartId

addToCart
: POST /cart/add

removeFromCart
: PATCH /cart/remove
updateCartQuantity: PATCH /cart/update
API Integration
[NEW] 

api.ts
Axios instance configuration.
Base URL: http://localhost:3000.
[NEW] 

cartService.ts
API call functions matching the controller endpoints.
UI Components
[NEW] 

CartPage.tsx
Main layout.
Fetches cart on mount.
Displays CartItem list or "Cart is empty" state.
Displays CartSummary.
[NEW] 

CartItem.tsx
Displays product info (image, name, price).
Quantity controls (+/-).
Remove button.
[NEW] 

CartSummary.tsx
Shows Subtotal and Total.
Checkout button.

